commitResults.messageTitle: Add increment Level-0 that prints hello and bye message
Add Increment Level-1 that functions like an echo server
commitResults.messageBody:
* Add custom welcome and farewell message
* Create function to pretty print messages
* Add loop that will interact and respond to user input

commitResults.messageTitle: Add Increment Level-2 that allows adding and printing of tasks
commitResults.messageBody:
* Add parsing of command from the user
* Add TaskManager.java to manage list of tasks, including adding and printing

commitResults.messageTitle: Add Increment Level-3 that allows marking of task as completed
commitResults.messageBody:
* Create Task.java to represent a task
* Add functionality to mark task as completed
* Update TaskManager.java to utilise new Task.java
* Add check-boxes to show status of task
* Handle missing and invalid arguments

commitResults.messageTitle: Add Increment A-CodingStandard that follows convention
commitResults.messageBody:
* Add line breaks before plus operators in welcome and exit message
* Create variables to store index of command and arguments

commitResults.messageTitle: Add Increment Level-4 that supports new task types
commitResults.messageBody:
* Update Task.java with task type icon
* Create Todo, Deadline, Event classes
* Update TaskManager.java to reflect new task type icon
* Implement new commands: todo, deadline, event
* Create CommandExecutioner class with improved parsing capabilities to support new commands
